messages.text: Promise you won’t go all Mom on me?
You’re meeting some weird boy in the graveyard.
Promise you’ll text me when you get there.
Maybe you should just go home.
Wait. I think I see him.
I feel like someone’s watching me.
Think it was just a reflection.
Let me know when you’re safe.
It’s fine. He’s smiling. Don’t know why I was so worried.
I have to go. Call you tomorrow.
You always do this. Call me first thing.
Remember how we said we’d always be there for each other, no matter what?
I need you. Tonight. Meet me at the graveyard @ 9.
Don’t know why I was so worried.
